clauses. ([Source code](https://github.com/bonfa/IfRemovingARealUseCase/blob/623019ec167ea7a0e6e5c0b0057d2bf8a83da9f1/src/main/java/it/fbonfadelli/hand_baggage/HandBaggageInformationFactory.java))

